<i>adverb</i>: 처참히 [처ː참히], 구차히 [구ː차히], 곤고히 [곤ː고히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>처참히 [처ː참히]</dt><br>
<dd>miserably; wretchedly</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 무서워 떨릴 정도로 슬프고 끔찍하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Sadly and dreadfully to such a degree that one trembles out of fear.</dd><br>
<dt>구차히 [구ː차히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. wretchedly</dd><br>
<dd>살림이 몹시 가난하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In poverty.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in a subservient manner</dd><br>
<dd>말과 행동이 당당하지 못하고 비굴하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Servily and ignobly in speaking and behaving.</dd><br>
<dt>곤고히 [곤ː고히]</dt><br>
<dd>miserably; wretchedly</dd><br>
<dd>형편이나 처지 등이 딱하고 어렵게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a state that one's situation or condition is miserable and hard.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>